                <div class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
                    <p>Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) is a neurodevelopmental condition that affects how you pay attention, manage impulses, and regulate activity levels. It's not a lack of willpower or intelligence, but a difference in brain wiring.</p>
                    <p>Living with ADHD can present unique challenges in areas like:</p>
